                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#100v">f. 100v</locus>
                           <desc type="DonationNote">Donation note.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘደጅአዝማች፡ ምራጭ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ለመቅደሰ፡
                              ጰራቅሊጦስ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መድኃኒተ፡ ነፍሱ፡ ወስመ፡ ክርስትናሁ፡ ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ ገብረ፡
                              አምላክ፡ ወእሙ፡ ወለተ፡ እግዚእ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ ወደቂቁ፡ ወለተ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ወለተ፡
                              ሃይማኖት፡ ወለተ፡ አረጋዊ፡ እግዚእ፡ ኃረያ፡ ወለተ፡ ጻድቃን፡ ወለተ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡
                              ለይኩን ... </q>
                           <foreign xml:lang="en">
                              This book is of <persName ref="PRS12938Merrac " role="donor"><roleName type="title">dağğʾāzmāč</roleName> Mǝrrāč̣</persName>
                              who donated it to the sanctuary of Ṗarāqliṭos so that it might be for
                              him salvation of his soul. His baptismal name is Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer,
                              the name of his father is Gabra ʾAmlāk, and his mother is Walatta
                              ʾƎgziʾ, and his wife Walatta Māryām, and his children Walatta
                              Takla-Hāymānot, Walatta Hāymānot, Walatta ʾAragāwi, ʾƎgziʾ Ḫaräya,
                              Walatta Ṣādǝqān, Walatta ʾIyasus. For ever and ever Amen. So be it
                              …</foreign>
                           
                        </item>
